Leading South African IT distributor Axiz is running a survey that investigates how companies are handling their video conferencing needs. Those who complete the survey stand a chance to win R2,000 by following these steps: The survey focuses on what video conferencing capabilities companies have, including the conferencing products they own – such as microphones and webcams. The survey also investigates whether these products are offering sufficient functionality for a company’s needs. The survey competition will end on 16 June 2021, so take the survey now to avoid missing out. Click here to take the survey.